# Fix Compilation Errors

## Goal Description
Resolve all compilation/runtime errors in both the NestJS backend and Angular frontend. This includes correcting Prisma import paths, creating missing NgRx store files, updating Angular configuration to use standalone providers, fixing Sass import deprecations, ensuring shared components (navbar/footer) are imported, typing HTTP responses in AuthService, and fixing the environment import for SocketService.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The plan adds new files under `src/app/store` and modifies several existing files. Please confirm that you are comfortable with these structural changes before we proceed.

